dialogue.speaker: Pointy-Haired Boss
dialogue.text: Uh-oh, I got an itch in my nose.

dialogue.speaker: Pointy-Haired Boss
dialogue.text: Can't scratch it now without looking unprofessional.

dialogue.speaker: Pointy-Haired Boss
dialogue.text: Maybe I can casually scratch it with one smooth gesture toward the easel.

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: There's a good chance they thought it was part of the presentation.

dialogue.speaker: Pointy-Haired Boss
dialogue.text: Did the paramedics remove the pointer or just tape over it?
